<doc id="355657" wikidata="Q15260780" url="?curid=355657" title="Nagoya, Saga">
<text>was the location of a castle in Matsuura District, Hizen Province, Japan. Today, the area is part of Chinzei in the city of Karatsu in Japan&#x27;s Saga prefecture.

Toyotomi Hideyoshi made Nagoya his base for directing the invasion of Korea.

