* &quot;Elf&quot; (2020) 
* &quot;Golden Girls&quot;
* The Rolling Stones 
* &quot;Ted Lasso&quot; (2022)
* RuPaul (2022)
* Buffalo Bills (2022)
* &quot;&quot; (2022)
